&gt;&gt;OH, WHAT IS THIS?
THIS LOOKS NICE.

00:02:27.819 --> 00:02:30.830
&gt;&gt;OH, THIS IS NETFLIX.
&gt;&gt;WILL BE THE HOME OF ALL LOUSY MOVIES!

00:02:30.830 --> 00:02:33.030
&gt;&gt;OH NO!
PLEASE!

00:02:33.030 --> 00:02:36.790
UH, TV REMOTES.
&gt;&gt;WILL HAVE HUNDRED OF BUTTONS THAT DO NOTHING.

00:02:36.790 --> 00:02:43.790
&gt;&gt;UH, YOUTUBE.
&gt;&gt;WILL LAUNCH THE CAREER OF JUSTIN BIEBER.

00:02:44.060 --> 00:02:48.099
&gt;&gt;NO!
PLEASE, I BEG YOU.

00:02:48.099 --> 00:02:52.500
&gt;&gt;NO, RELAX FELIX.
TOGETHER OUR INVENTIONS WILL CHANGE THE WORLD.

00:02:52.500 --> 00:02:55.580
&gt;&gt;WELL AT LEAST I STILL HAVE ONE
INVENTION SO SIMPLE

00:02:55.580 --> 00:02:59.129
